## Context Loading Rules

Read files based on task complexity:

| Task Type | Read First |
|-----------|------------|
| Content tweak (copy edit) | Target file only |
| Single component edit | Target file + design tokens config |
| Multi-component work | Target files + relevant layout / framework config |
| New feature from task list | Planning doc + linked design spec |
| Architecture change | `CLAUDE.md` + planning doc + every file the change touches |
| Anything brand / voice / copy related | Content doc + design doc |

**Single source of truth per fact.** Stack decisions, content plan, brand voice/design, and deploy procedures each live in ONE doc; other docs reference. Current session state lives in the handoff doc ONLY.

